{{Use dmy dates|date=June 2013}} {{Infobox person | name = Henri Colson | image = | image_size = 150px | alt = | caption = | birth_name = Henri Jean Colson | birth_date = {{birth date|df=yes|1819|4|21}} | birth_place = [[Ghent]], [[Belgium]] | death_date = {{death date and age|df=yes|1900|4|30|1819|4|21}} | death_place = | nationality = [[Belgian people|Belgian]] | other_names = | known_for = | occupation = engineer, industrialist, professor, politician }} '''Henri Jean Colson''' (21 April 1819 &ndash; 30 April 1900) was a [[Belgium|Belgian]] engineer, industrialist, professor at the [[University of Ghent]], [[alderman]] and [[burgomaster]] of [[Ghent]] ([[Belgium]]) (''ad interim'')
